          { en: "If I <span class='key'>had</span> enough time and money, I <span class='key'>would travel</span> around the world.", jp: "もし時間とお金が十分あれば、世界中を旅するのに。" },
        ],
        formula: "If + S + <span class='accent'>動詞の過去形</span>, S + <span class='accent'>would[could/might]</span> + 動詞の原形"
